# Invoices Folder

Invoice records (sent and received).

## Example: Outgoing Invoice

```markdown
---
type: invoice
invoice_number: INV-2026-001
issue_date: 2026-02-28
due_date: 2026-03-15
amount: 500.00
currency: USD
customer: Client A
status: paid
---

## Invoice Details

- **Number:** INV-2026-001
- **Customer:** Client A
- **Issue Date:** 2026-02-28
- **Due Date:** 2026-03-15
- **Amount:** $500.00

## Line Items

| Description | Quantity | Unit Price | Total |
|-------------|----------|------------|-------|
| AI Consulting (Feb 2026) | 1 | $500 | $500 |

## Payment Status

- [x] Invoice sent: 2026-02-28
- [x] Payment received: 2026-03-05
- [x] Recorded in Accounting

## Linked Files

- PDF: /Invoices/2026-02/INV-2026-001.pdf
- Accounting Entry: /Accounting/2026-03/transaction_001.md
```

## Example: Incoming Invoice (Bill)

```markdown
---
type: bill
invoice_number: BILL-456
issue_date: 2026-03-01
due_date: 2026-03-30
amount: 200.00
currency: USD
vendor: Software Inc
category: software_subscription
status: pending
---

## Bill Details

- **Vendor:** Software Inc
- **Service:** Annual SaaS Subscription
- **Due Date:** 2026-03-30
- **Amount:** $200.00

## Approval Workflow

- [x] Received and logged
- [ ] Pending approval
- [ ] Scheduled for payment
- [ ] Paid

## Budget Category

Operating Expenses → Software & Tools
